      • calcServerStopped

        public java.util.Date calcServerStopped(long staleRecordTimeout)
        Returns server stop date that may be approximate. Returns explicit (precise) stop date if ConnectionStopped is not null. Otherwise returns LastUpdate date if it is less than CurrentTime - staleRecordTimeout (i.e. the server is considered to be killed).
        Parameters:
        staleRecordTimeout - stale record timeout in milliseconds.
        Returns:
        server stop date (that may be approximate) or null if the server is running
